        public static void execute()
                    throws LostConnectionException
        Performs tasks associated with the initialization of the data layer. This includes setting up the data store, the connection pool, and the maintenance process.
        Throws:
        LostConnectionException - Is thrown if a connection could not be established to the data store to perform the initialization.
